    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279440/extras/a4d2979a529c0d0c264b247a81b1023a.poster.avif?t=1768862014\" width=720 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279440/extras/a4d2979a529c0d0c264b247a81b1023a.webm?t=1768862014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279440/extras/a4d2979a529c0d0c264b247a81b1023a.mp4?t=1768862014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >未来无人机空中炮艇</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Drone Sector</strong> 将空中炮艇的近距离空中支援与无人机的观察与任务指挥相结合。受现实中的AC-130空中炮艇和MQ-9“死神”无人机启发，它在未来背景下融合了这些强大角色，在先进技术与更强大的火力支持下，让你能够执行更加复杂和危险的任务。虽然它不是纯粹的军事模拟游戏，但重点仍然放在战术规划与执行上，并且在任务设计和武器装备上有更多的灵活性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279440/extras/954792dda18d93477e8de9294b18fc07.poster.avif?t=1768862014\" width=720 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279440/extras/954792dda18d93477e8de9294b18fc07.webm?t=1768862014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279440/extras/954792dda18d93477e8de9294b18fc07.mp4?t=1768862014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >任务控制</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >引导你的小队在充满敌意的环境中推进，完成任务目标。精准指挥，帮助他们避开陷阱，并用压倒性的火力消灭高优先级目标。面对数量上占优的敌军，你需要最大化利用技术优势扭转局势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279440/extras/b6caccc65c88993209933f5bc1df23e2.poster.avif?t=1768862014\" width=720 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279440/extras/b6caccc65c88993209933f5bc1df23e2.webm?t=1768862014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279440/extras/b6caccc65c88993209933f5bc1df23e2.mp4?t=1768862014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >任务间的进展</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每个任务中，你需要做出战略决策来收集资源。派遣地面小队进入建筑物或关键区域收集重要资源和研究文件，但这伴随着风险。停留太久，你的小队可能会被压倒性的敌军消灭。决定何时撤离，以及何时冒险以获取有价值的奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在任务间的基地中，升级你的空中炮艇、小队和武器。管理弹药生产并研究新技术，以提高你在战场上的胜算。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279440/extras/6f72fe1d77f860c36d88e1a3ba861510.poster.avif?t=1768862014\" width=720 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279440/extras/6f72fe1d77f860c36d88e1a3ba861510.webm?t=1768862014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279440/extras/6f72fe1d77f860c36d88e1a3ba861510.mp4?t=1768862014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >流畅、灵敏的空中炮艇武器控制</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种视角模式：彩色、夜视和热成像</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >指挥地面上的自给自足小队</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种步兵与装甲单位类型</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >资源收集与弹药管理</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武器研究与制造</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小队组建与升级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精心设计的关卡与随机生成的任务</p></li></ul>",
